title: Datalatte.ai
body:
We empower internet users to monetize their own data and provide data scientists with access to non-identifiable users’ data using AI Feature Store at an affordable price.

## Full Proposal
https://port.oceanprotocol.com/t/datalatte-ai-oceandao-round-9/869

## Grant Deliverables
[ ] Grant Deliverable 1: Conduction of user interviews and design of DApp
[ ] Grant Deliverable 2: Development of an AI Feature Store PoC and setting up of a Datalatte marketplace
[ ] Grant Deliverable 3: Creation of a real-world use case to underpin the fundamental features of Datalattee and communicating the content through multi-channels (Medium, Twitter, and LinkedIn).
